    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Living out of a shed in the middle of nowhere, Rolus is always down on his luck. Today his tummy rumbles, but without a cent to his name, he's got to find a way to eat. Luckily for him, there's a fast-food restaurant right down the street. He finds himself dumpster diving, looking for any scraps, when suddenly a meteorite comes down from above—crashing into both him and the dumpster!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282620/extras/715adc12cacbd98db12202776b0bb342.poster.avif?t=1744711585\" width=480 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282620/extras/715adc12cacbd98db12202776b0bb342.webm?t=1744711585\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282620/extras/715adc12cacbd98db12202776b0bb342.mp4?t=1744711585\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join Rolus and his newfound friend, as they try to scrounge up change to finally buy the fated dollar-menu cheeseburger. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >This Demo features...</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Entire First Chapter</strong> <strong>-</strong> Including several areas to explore, items to collect, strange folk to meet, and secrets to uncover! (Roughly 1 hour of content to enjoy)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Top-Down Combat -</strong> go around shooting ducks, junkies and gnomes  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Freaks and Weirdos -</strong> come face to face with the Outskirts' best, deal with their troubles in anyway you can, in exchange for measly pennies.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Hand-drawn Graphics -</strong> expressive art reminiscent of flash cartoons from the 2000s </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Original Soundtrack -</strong> home-recorded by PostElvis, filled with eclectic genres, ranging from garage punk to ambient to folk.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282620/extras/aedb3da5ba3f1496e1922e6e05d85172.poster.avif?t=1744711585\" width=450 height=276 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282620/extras/aedb3da5ba3f1496e1922e6e05d85172.webm?t=1744711585\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3282620/extras/aedb3da5ba3f1496e1922e6e05d85172.mp4?t=1744711585\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul>",
